# Agent & workflow rules

- All LLM calls go through `lib/ai.ts` with `tier: 'fast' | 'strong'` and `evalkit.step` metadata
- Use AI SDK v6: `generateText` + `Output.object({ schema })` for structured output
- Store prompt version hash from `lib/prompts.ts` on the run record
- Workflow steps use `"use step"`; orchestrator uses `"use workflow"` in `workflows/eval-run.ts`
- Each step calls `updateRun(runId, patch)` for progress visibility
- Unit tests mock via `lib/test/mock-ai.ts` — assert Zod shape and category distribution, not exact text
